originalText.text: Go to Caitlin Fontanez! Caitlin is not only highly professional but also incredibly knowledgeable. She took the time to assess my skin and discuss any concerns or preferences I had. Her gentle touch and attention to detail made me feel at ease. She is also funny and lovely to spend time with!

originalText.text:
Visited Plump last month to get the LaseMD laser treatment for the first time.  I’m not someone who does a lot of cosmetic treatments but starting to try and be more proactive about my fine lines and sunspots.I couldn’t be more happy with the results of this treatment…worth every penny.

I saw nurse Amy Lee who is amazing and walked me through what to expect during the treatment + post care recovery.  The beauty of this laser is that there’s little downtime for recovery…my skin did purge and create a sandpaper-like texture for a few days but it was only noticeable to the touch and I never felt like I needed to apply makeup to cover anything up. By day 7 post treatment my skin fully healed and has never looked/felt better! Def would say this is something I’m going to try and add into my skin spa routine now.

originalText.text: Although I wasn’t able to have my lip fillers done due to medical reasons, I was very pleased with my visit. The office was super clean and chic. Front desk was a doll. She offered me water when she realized I was a bit nervous. Rn Lee was super sweet and informative too. Hopefully I will be back in the future:)

originalText.text: I had a really great experience with Amy Lee! She took the time to educate me on the difference between .25cc and .5cc lip filler and gave her opinion on what the best option would be for me based on our consultation. We opted for the .25cc even tho I booked for the half which really speaks to Amy’s priorities of clients needs/wants versus the dollar amount of the service and I really appreciated that. I also got Botox for the first time. I was nervously because I still wanted some movement with my eyebrows and facial expressions but she walked me through my options and I’m super happy I trusted her. My lips are perfectly naturally plump and my forehead is free of wrinkles while also being flexible enough for my comfort. I will absolutely be seeing Amy for all my future services!
